<p>I don't think the Factory in-universe would have a logo. To my understanding or at least in my canon &quot;The Factory&quot; just refers to a set of items that have been sourced or are believed to have originated from some eldritch manufacturing entity. If anything they might have a <em>mark</em> of some kind.</p>

